Timeshyft, just after firing the eight ferrous iron from his gauss rifle, 
reloaded his weapon. If he could just maul the autobot, and then go away, 
the pain he would cause would be enough to satisfy him. That, on the other 
hand, was easier said than done. Jetfire was renowned to be one of the 
toughest of the Autobot warriors. Victory over him would also bring him 
great glory among the Decepticon ranks.
